  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to identify the expression signature of miR-181a, miR-196a and miR-21 in
      plasma of SLE patients and difference in their expression among groups with different
      systemic lupus erythematosis disease activity index (SLEDAI) scores.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
